    {
      "order": 2,
      "instruction": "Whisk Dry ingredients in a bowl."
    },
    {
      "order": 3,
      "instruction": "Add Wet Ingredients, including all the liquid in the canned corn kernels. Mix well."
    },
    {
      "order": 4,
      "instruction": "Pour into a 2-2.5 quart / 2-2.5 litre / 8 cup casserole dish."
    },
    {
      "order": 5,
      "instruction": "Bake for 55 - 60 minutes (standard ovens) or 50 minutes (fan forced / convection), or until set but still a bit jiggle in the centre (it will set when cooled). The top should be a deep golden brown."
